Package org.digidoc4j.impl.asic.validation

Class ReportedMessagesExtractor

java.lang.Object
org.digidoc4j.impl.asic.validation.ReportedMessagesExtractor
public class ReportedMessagesExtractor extends Object
A helper class for extracting token validation messages from DSS SimpleReports.

  • Nested Class Summary

    Nested Classes
    Modifier and Type
    Class
    Description
    static class 
    ReportedMessagesExtractor.Message
    An immutable encapsulation for the key (message tag) and the value (message text) of a single error/warning message, and the ID of the token where this message originated from.
